{
  "stem": "21978.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it didn't come to it that my sister and her family could come to Kenya.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we were-- we knew that eventually, there will be the independence in Kenya.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that wouldn't have been good for newcomers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We thought of immigrating to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But my brother-in-law didn't like the idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was not happy in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was elder-- older than my sister, much older than my sister-- and used to a better life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in, in Israel, he was working in kibbutz in, in the, with horse, with stable and tractor driver.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he did think that he would start again somewhere like-- you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we eventually got the idea that we will come to Australia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then my sister and her family came, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I was separated from my sister for eight years, but not completely separated because she came to visit us twice, once with her daughter.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And her daughter is the same age as my Naomi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Her, her daughter's name is Daphne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they looked like twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when Annetta came to visit us in Kenya, she walked in a pram.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The little one was, I think, 18 months old, both of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they looked like twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were both blonde.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We dressed them the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And somebody met my sister and said, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Heller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I didn't know you have twins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm not Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Heller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they are not twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then my husband had to come to rescue to tell them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then we met-- Annetta met my dentist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he said-- she walked with my husband on the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And dentist said, Robert, I know this is your wife today.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You can't tell me that this is your sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
